snippet.title: Film Companion
snippet.description:
Welcome to Film Companion’s channel, your #1 platform for the top videos from the world of entertainment. Film Companion is India’s premium movie portal.

Here you’ll find the latest interviews with your favourite stars like Shah Rukh Khan, Salman Khan, Priyanka Chopra, Deepika Padukone, Anurag Kashyap, Imtiaz Ali, video essays, film festival coverage, on-location stories, recommendations, latest movie trailers and much more - in short, everything you need to enhance your cinematic experience.

If you love pop culture and writing about it, then here's your chance to publish stories with Film Companion! Introducing #ReadersWrite where you can submit your stories. So get set, submit: https://bit.ly/2KaCvBL

Connect with us on Telegram here: https://t.me/FilmCompanionNews
